- Petra: Warp from this run (max. 4h) can be carried over to the next run
- Transport Plan Cache Timeout: Sometimes transport plan cache can become stale. This will force clear the cache after the specified number of seconds

- Atlas Mountains: +5 civilization idea point. All buildings within 3 tile range get +X Production Multiplier. X = number of different resources produced but not consumed within the range
- Festival of Tanit: Atlas Mountains get +3 range and also provide Building Level Boost